      "text": " <username>nishiohirokazu</username>",
      "created": 1241535600,
      "updated": 1241535600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d10cf",
      "text": " <body>いやー、ペアを組む相手のプレイに怒り狂いそうで(ぉ</body>",
      "created": 1241535600,
      "updated": 1241535600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
