      "created": 1241535600,
      "updated": 1241535600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d10d2",
      "text": " <comment>",
      "created": 1241535600,
      "updated": 1241535600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d10d3",
      "text": " <username>Dubhead</username>",
      "created": 1241535600,
      "updated": 1241535600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d10d4",
      "text": " <body>ゲームの面白さの一つに共同作業の面白さってものもあるんじゃないかなー。一人用RPGとMMORPGの面白さが違う的な何かが。まあ向き不向きはあると思います。</body>",
